{"tid":1128224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(財務自由) 究竟啲武俠係點搵食？","createTime":"2019-04-27T16:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-28T08:32:15.000Z","uid":45206,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b85e408ccedf76c19701bbb6d61c6372bf758e65","tid":1128224,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"啲武俠日日無所事事 但又經常出手闊綽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到佢哋係靠乜嘢維生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我一直都覺得應該同以前啲黑社會一樣靠收陀地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即係 娥媚山下面嗰幾條村 好可能就係娥媚派睇嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買菜嗰個八婆蓮每個月就要畀陀地咁樣樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到啲酒家 大叫一聲：小二上最好嘅菜！<br />\n呢個情形好可能其實係威脅緊個小二<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食完根本唔使找數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係諗到咁多 有冇巴打有idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee6ffaed185812d1ca185df510ecadcab48a80a","tid":1128224,"uid":144001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"打汪洋大盜攞懸紅<br />\n運鏢保鑣"},{"pid":"b15af92aee86bc07187f90e380bb3bbf39194ef3","tid":1128224,"uid":35814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T16:30:21.000Z","msg":"射鵰四大高手入面<br />\n<br />\n黃藥師開班教完四個學生都可以有成個島<br />\n有班奴僕，仲可以養左周伯通一段時間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐陽鋒睇個勢應該係黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一燈呢啲話晒都做和尚有香油錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係洪七公實在啲貼地啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62972d7b2ffc173006c928b13c605884db66ff68","tid":1128224,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b15af92aee86bc